# Cloudflare Pages headers.
# Cross-origin isolation → SharedArrayBuffer → multi-threaded onnxruntime-web
# (SOD ~10–15s instead of ~60s). MUST be present or the SOD drops to 1 thread.
# COEP `credentialless` still lets the jsDelivr ORT runtime + the R2/CDN model load.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless

# Content-hashed build assets — cache hard.
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
